description	"Remnant Jumptrooper

^2Weaponry:
- EC-17 Holdout Blaster Pistol (2)
- Imperial Heavy Repeater

^8Attributes:
- Jetpack
-- No Overheat
- Fuel (2)
- Reinforcements (2)
- Assemble (1)

Some of the more experienced stormtroopers were equipped with jetpacks. These particular models can sustain flight for longer durations, but cannot recharge."